    "body": "This is known, and has been reported many times. It's not a code issue, but more of a social one: there is no incentive to run `lightserv` nodes, so it is done on a volunteer basis.\r\n\r\nThe simplest course of action is to wait.\r\n\r\nAn (experimental, paid) alternative is to use the [`vipnode`](https://vipnode.shazow.net/) service.\r\n\r\n-----\r\n\r\nSuggest closing issue as not actionable.",
